org.apache.ambari.server.controller

Class AlertDefinitionResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.controller.AlertDefinitionResponse

  • public class AlertDefinitionResponse
extends Object
    The AlertDefinitionResponse encapsulates the definition information that should be serialized and returned in REST requests for alerts, groups, and targets.
